      "writtenOn": "2020-03-23T18:50:14Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "When parameterizing a test, it is recommended to *not* have if statements here. Otherwise the test is testing a mix of success and error cases. I find that confusing.\n\ngo/tott/572",
